'''Nkyidwo Afahyɛ''' yɛ afehyia [[afahyɛ]] a ahenfo ne wɔn manafo a wɔn Essumeja wɔ Bekwai mpesoa so a ɛwɔ Asante Mantam wɔ Ghana no di. Wodi afahye yi wɔ dwoada a etwa toɔ wɔ bosome a ɛtɔ so du biako anaa bosome a etwa toɔ no mu<ref>https://ghanaemberlin.de/travel-tourism/festival/</ref><ref>https://www.easytrackghana.com/cultural-overview-ghana-festivals.php</ref><ref>http://accra.rockvilleplace.com/ashanti-region/</ref>.

== Afahyɛ ==
Ahenfo no bɔ dwa data ma wɔyɛ amammere ahorrɔw wɔ Asantemanso kwae no mu, faako a wogyedi sɛ ɛyɛ asantefo nsamanpɔw mu. Amanfo no kankye abaosom no ma nhyira, nkwa tenten ne ahobammɔ<ref name="touringghana.com">https://touringghana.com/festivals/</ref>.

== Mfasoɔ ==
Wodi saa afahye yi de kae Asantefo nsɔn a wodikan, a wɔkeyerɛ sɛ wofiri tokro kɛseɛ bi mu wɔ asase ase maa ɛno nti, ɛhɔ bɛyɛɛ Asantefo fibea. Wɔkyerɛ sɛ, saa nsɛm yi sii wɔ dwoada ahemaakye a na kraman ne gyata di won akyi<ref name="touringghana.com"/><ref>https://www.slutchtours.com/?page_id=21</ref>.

